t: "Calling upon Him Ë¹aloneËº is the truth. But those Ë¹idolsËº the pagans invoke besides Him Ë¹canËº never respond to them in any way. Ë¹It isËº just like someone who stretches out their hands to water, Ë¹asking itËº to reach their mouths, but it can never do so. The calls of the disbelievers are only in vain"